WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.550 --> 00:00:05.610
- If you're following a nutrition program

00:00:05.610 --> 00:00:09.810
that is designed to trigger
the physiological effect

00:00:09.810 --> 00:00:11.930
of ketogenesis in the body,

00:00:11.930 --> 00:00:16.930
you've probably used butter or MCT oil.

00:00:17.220 --> 00:00:18.600
Mixed it all together.

00:00:18.600 --> 00:00:20.730
Maybe some electrolytes also.

00:00:20.730 --> 00:00:23.540
Whether you travel or you just
prepare that kind of thing

00:00:23.540 --> 00:00:25.490
at your kitchen counter,

00:00:25.490 --> 00:00:27.570
those are a lot of different ingredients,

00:00:27.570 --> 00:00:29.860
as some of them can be kind of a mess.

00:00:29.860 --> 00:00:32.180
We developed IN-Perium

00:00:32.180 --> 00:00:35.320
which has MCT oil

00:00:35.320 --> 00:00:37.970
in a small enough volume

00:00:37.970 --> 00:00:41.790
that it won't knock you out of autophagy

00:00:41.790 --> 00:00:43.270
and out of a fasted state.

00:00:43.270 --> 00:00:44.860
So that's really important.

00:00:44.860 --> 00:00:48.500
While at the same time
providing 200 milligrams

00:00:48.500 --> 00:00:52.870
of caffeine so that you get
the appetite suppression

00:00:52.870 --> 00:00:53.703
with the caffeine.

00:00:53.703 --> 00:00:57.210
And the MCT which also slows down

00:00:57.210 --> 00:00:59.860
the absorption of the caffeine.

00:00:59.860 --> 00:01:02.310
And then at the same time
we added some electrolytes

00:01:02.310 --> 00:01:03.810
without a salty taste.

00:01:03.810 --> 00:01:05.820
And then sweetened with stevia

00:01:05.820 --> 00:01:08.460
which doesn't create an insulin response.

00:01:08.460 --> 00:01:10.800
So a lot of different bases were covered

00:01:10.800 --> 00:01:13.230
so that we have a great supplement

00:01:13.230 --> 00:01:16.000
that supports fasted periods,

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:18.810
that supports the ketogenic process,

00:01:18.810 --> 00:01:20.500
the function of the human body.

00:01:20.500 --> 00:01:22.690
Keeps your appetite
suppressed so that you can be

00:01:22.690 --> 00:01:25.922
in the fasted state longer
and stay high energy.

